**CTC (Cost to Company)** is the total annual employment cost, including your salary, allowances, and employer contributions to PF and gratuity. Your **in-hand salary** (take-home) is significantly lower after deducting: employee PF (12% of basic), professional tax (₹200–2,500/year), TDS on salary (based on tax regime and declarations), and HRA may or may not be exempted depending on rent paid.
